  "encoding": "windows-1252",
  "html": "\n<div><center>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><font><img src=\"../images/R.gif\"/> </font><b>Burning\n        burning burning ...</b><hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p>The complete text of the Buddha's Fire Sermon (which\n        corresponds in importance to the Sermon on the Mount)\n        from which these words are taken, will be found\n        translated in the late Henry Clarke Warren's <i>Buddhism\n        in Translation </i>(Harvard Oriental Series). Mr. Warren\n        was one of the great pioneers of Buddhist studies in the\n        Occident. [Eliot's note]</p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"kassapaB.htm\">Kassapa the Fire\n                Worshipper</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"title_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"matthew5-7.htm\">Christ's Sermon on\n                the Mount see <i>Matthew</i> 5-7</a></td>\n<td><a href=\"title_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Waste_A.htm\"><font>back to \"The Waste Land\" </font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center></div>\n",
  "text": "Burning burning burning ... The complete text of the Buddha's Fire Sermon (which corresponds in importance to the Sermon on the Mount) from which these words are taken, will be found translated in the late Henry Clarke Warren's Buddhism in Translation (Harvard Oriental Series). Mr. Warren was one of the great pioneers of Buddhist studies in the Occident. [Eliot's note] Kassapa the Fire Worshipper Christ's Sermon on the Mount see Matthew 5-7 back to \"The Waste Land\"",
